There is similar flow when it comes to solutions of Shopify SaaS applications. They all leverage the same futures of Shopify platform.
With 2021, Shopify released [Online Store 2.0](https://shopify.dev/docs/themes/os20) which introduces new theme architecture. Biggest change was template files started using JSON format to insert sections to the page.
Shopify wants and forces you to follow these new tools